messages.subject: Harvest Moon 64

messages.messageBody:
Sandra Dodd:

A while ago, you posted something about Harvest Moon games for NES. I was
reading on the Nintendo website that Harvest Moon 64 for N64 will be coming
out this summer. I was reading about the game, it really sounds like a great
game to play. I am planning on getting this one for my son.

Also, Poke'mon Snap for N64 will be released on July 26, 1999. I have been
waiting for this one. I almost be a gameboy for son to be able to play this
game. I am glad that I waited, now I can spend the money the games instead.

Asmaa
